So what is Meet23?

Meet23 is a survey created by the{' '} Datamatch {' '} team for the Class of 2023. It’s a simple process: sign up, fill out a survey, and get matched via The Algorithm™ with other freshmen to meet! As FRIENDS. Unless…. 😉

And… who are you?

Hi! Hello! This website is not a scam. We’re Harvard students, and every February, we run a very serious matchmaking tradition called{' '} Datamatch , last year with over 27,000 users and 14 colleges! Our team got bored over the summer, so we decided to make this. We are the real people who appear in the real photo below!

So how accurate are these results?

Extremely. But though we can play (platonic) Cupid, we can't play God! It's up to you to contact your matches, and actually make something happen. ""You miss 100% of the shots you don't take." - Wayne Gretzky" - Michael Scott

Something’s not working!!!!

AHHHHHH. AHHHHHHHHHH. aAHHHHHHHHHHHHHHH. Yeah, it’s our first year trying this out, our bad. Luckily, we hired a monkey to help you by mashing random keys if you have questions or errors. Just email hcsdatamatch@gmail.com.

Any other advice for freshman year?

Make new friends. Tie some yarn. And that’s how you do the Scarn!

Who are you?

Hi! Hello! This website is not a scam. We run a very serious matchmaking service every February called{' '} Datamatch . Our team got bored over the summer, so we decided to make this. We are the real people who appear in the real photo below!

So what is Meet23?

It’s a simple process: sign up, fill out a survey, and get matched via The Algorithm™ with other freshmen to meet! As FRIENDS. Unless….{' '} 😉

Why are the questions so funny?

With our (patent pending) state of the art technology, we have dissected the true humor of the average Harvard freshman populace. Combined with the majestic brain-power of Upperclassmen trying to relive their glorious Freshmen lives, this survey has been birthed.

Something’s not working!!!!

AHHHHHH. AHHHHHHHHHH. aAHHHHHHHHHHHHHHH. Yeah, it’s our first year trying this out, our bad. Luckily, we hired a monkey to help you by mashing random keys if you have questions or errors. Just email hcsdatamatch@gmail.com.

Let's just get straight to it. Is the Algorithm™ random?

It can be anything you want it to be.

Okay, I get it. It's "proprietary artificial intelligence." *wink wink*

No, really! Though in the past less scrupulous HCS members have resorted to rolling 20-sided dice and examining the entrails of slaughtered animals, the modern Datamatch survey is fundamentally rooted in strong data analysis.

So how accurate are these results?

Extremely. But though we can play (platonic) Cupid, we can't play God! It's up to you to contact your matches, and actually make something happen. ""You miss 100% of the shots you don't take." - Wayne Gretzky" - Michael Scott

I want to be a part of this!

OOOH YES! Become a Datamatch cupid! Just fill in your email and we’ll reach out to you:

Any other advice for freshman year?

Make new friends. Tie some yarn. And that’s how you do the Scarn!
Love, The Meet23 Team
